rem --- Lot/Serial Transaction History By Customer Report (Report)
rem --- Program ivr_lotcusthist_o1.aon v8.0.0 16Jul2007 (ivr_9b)
rem --- Created by adx_codeport.bbx v1.1.5 (07/16/2007 03:04:37)

